summary: The video shows a family preparing and eating meals. Breakfast consists of blueberry muffins and milk. Lunch includes dal, rice, and parsley. For dinner, the family has lamb kebabs, roasted tomatoes, couscous, Greek salad, pita chips, and hummus.
transcript: What my 10 kids ate today.. What my 10 kids ate today.. for breakfast they ate blueberry muffins and milk.. for lunch they ate dal which is an Indian lentil dish with rice and parsley.. and for dinner they ate lamb kebabs roasted tomatoes couscous Greek salad pita chips and hummus.. Happy eating
